      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must hold ISO 9001 certification and maintain a verified test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver holds a vendor quality certificate but lacks an independently audited test suite for hemolysis-relevant turbulent shear flows. Achieved level 2 against required level 4; gap remains open."
