      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical rotating-flow benchmarks must confirm solver achieves stated spatial and temporal order at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed on a lid-driven cavity but not on rotating-frame or curved-channel flows representative of the pump geometry. Achieved level 2; required level 4."
